curam.util.dataaccess
Class KeyRepository.EntityKeyInfo

java.lang.Object
  curam.util.dataaccess.KeyRepository.EntityKeyInfo
Enclosing class:
KeyRepository
public static class KeyRepository.EntityKeyInfo
extends java.lang.Object

Class containing key information from the most recently insert instance of an application entity. You can look up the most recent instance via the KeyRepository class. There is only one instance (the most recent) per entity, so once you have a reference to the EntityKeyInfo for an entity, you do not need to look it up again -- the values in the instance you hold will change after inserts on the named entity.
